root: ^You win. I suppose I have to let you walk free.
^Nice one, my servant. I knew you could do it.
^Can we really just walk out? You won't try to stab us as we're leaving?
^No, we won't kill you. You have my word, my men won't touch you.
^I thought we were free to go?
^I would like to discuss something with you.
^> The Mafia Boss looks at you in particular
